Privacy Policy for Apps
Privacy Policy
Effective Date: May 28, 2024
Mesut Usta ("we," "us," or "our") operates the Watch Face mobile application (the "Service").
This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data.
Information We Collect
We do not collect any personal information from you when you use our Service.
Use of Your Data
Since we do not collect any personal information, we do not use any personal data for any purpose.
Disclosure of Your Data
We do not disclose your data to third parties.
Security
We are committed to protecting your personal data. We have implemented various security measures to protect your data, including:
Data encryption: We encrypt your data at rest and in transit.
Access controls: We restrict access to your data to authorized personnel.
Security audits: We regularly conduct security audits to identify and address any potential vulnerabilities.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at ustamesut@gmail.com
By using our Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
